description: "Query: clickbench_q22"
---
+---------------+----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |
+---------------+----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | BytesProcessedNode                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |
|               |   Federated                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |
|               |  Limit: skip=0, fetch=10                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |
|               |   Sort: c DESC NULLS FIRST                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |
|               |     Projection: hits.SearchPhrase, min(hits.URL), count(Int64(1)) AS c                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |
|               |       Aggregate: groupBy=[[hits.SearchPhrase]], aggr=[[min(hits.URL), count(Int64(1))]]                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |
|               |         Filter: CAST(hits.SearchPhrase AS Utf8View) != Utf8("")                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |
|               |           TableScan: hits projection=[URL, SearchPhrase], full_filters=[hits.URL LIKE Utf8("%google%")]                                                                                                                                                                                                              |
| physical_plan | BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |
|               |   SchemaCastScanExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |
|               |     CooperativeExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |
|               |       VirtualExecutionPlan name=duckdb compute_context=:memory: initial_sql=SELECT "hits"."SearchPhrase", min("hits"."URL"), count(1) AS "c" FROM "hits" WHERE (CAST("hits"."SearchPhrase" AS VARCHAR) <> '') AND "hits"."URL" LIKE '%google%' GROUP BY "hits"."SearchPhrase" ORDER BY "c" DESC NULLS FIRST LIMIT 10 |
|               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |
+---------------+----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
